        "text_CcwiLn": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Sandro Petrillo is part artist, part alchemist, part orchestrator of experience. Fascinated by how atmosphere can create connection, his work starts with the senses;  inviting you to take notice and be present in the moment. We caught up with the <a href=\"https://www.sssoaps.co/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">SSSOAPS</span></a> founder and Toronto dance music scene veteran to talk multisensory design, daily rituals, and bringing feels to the forefront.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
